.TH mbimapidle 1 "@DATE@" "mbimapidle (@VERSION@)" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
mbimapidle \- Maintain persistent server connection using IMAP protocol (RFC 2177) IDLE extension and execute sync command on new messages.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "mbimapidle"
.br
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B mbimapidle
.SH "CONFIGURATION FILE"
.TP
The configuration file should be located at

.I $XDG_CONFIG_DIR/mbimapidle/mbimapidlerc

.SH AUTHOR
Ali Abdallah (ali.abdallah@suse.com)
